quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  6,91,aur un logon ne khuda ki qader jaisi jaan-ni chahiye thi nah jani. jab unhon ne kaha ke khuda ne ensaan par ( wahi aur kitaab waghera ) kuch bhi nazil nahikiya. kaho jo kitaab moose le kar aeye they usay kis ne nazilkiya tha jo logon ke liye noor aur hadaayat thi aur jisay tum ne alehda alehda ourak ( par naqal ) kar rakha hai un ( ke kuch hissay ) ko to zahir karte ho aur aksar ko chupatay ho. aur tum ko woh baatein sikhayi gayeen jin ko nah tum jantay they aur nah tumahray baap dada. keh do ( is kitaab ko ) khuda hi ne ( nazilkiya tha ) phir un ko chore diya ke apni behooda bakwaas mein khailtay rahen
  6,92,aur ( waisi hi ) yeh kitaab hai jisay hum ne nazilkiya hai babarkat jo apne se pehli ( kitabon ) ki tasdeeq karti hai aur ( jo ) is liye ( nazil ki gayi hai ) ke tum mukkay aur is ke aas paas ke logon ko aagah kardo. aur jo log akhirat par imaan rakhtay hain woh is kitaab par bhi imaan rakhtay hain aur woh apni namazon ki poori khabar rakhtay hain
  6,93,aur is se barh kar zalim kon hoga jo khuda par jhoot iftira kere. ya yeh kahe ke mujh par wahi aayi hai halaank is par kuch bhi wahi nah aayi ho aur jo yeh kahe ke jis terhan ki kitaab khuda ne nazil ki hai is terhan ki mein bhi bana laita hon. aur kash tum un zalim ( yani mushriq ) logon ko is waqt dekho jab mout ki sakhtiyon mein ( mubtala ) hon aur farishtay ( un ki taraf azaab ke liye ) haath barha rahay hon ke nikalu apni jaanen. aaj tum ko zillat ke azaab ki saza di jaye gi is liye ke tum khuda par jhoot bola karte they aur is ki ayaton se sar kashi karte they
  6,94,aur jaissa hum ne tum ko pehli dafaa pedakiya tha aisa hi aaj akailey akailey hamaray paas aeye aur jo ( maal o mata'a) hum ne tumhe ataa farmaya tha woh sab apni peeth peechay chore aeye aur hum tumahray sath tumahray sifarshion ko bhi nahi dekhte jin ki nisbat tum khayaal karte they ke woh tumahray ( Shafi aur hamaray ) shareek hain. ( aaj ) tumahray aapas ke sab taluqaat munhqita hogaye aur jo daaway tumkiya karte they sab jatay rahay
